condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :PA, Section I, Part C, Para 1b | Description :Before initiating land acquisition or displacement of people, makeavailable compensation, relocate and rehabilitate Displaced Persons | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :PA, Section I, Part C, para 1c | Description :Whenever required, proceed to have an additional RAP(s) preparedsatisfactory to the Bank, submitted for review and approval of theBank, disclose RAP publicly; implement RAP | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :PA, Section I, Part C, paras 4&5 | Description :Maintain adequate procedures to enable M&E; regularly collect,compile and submit to the Bank information on the status of compliance with safeguards | Frequency :SemiAnnual

Finance Agreement :PA, Section I, Part D, Para 2 | Description :Six months prior to the completion of each ports under the Project,the Project Implementing Entity, through Xia’pu County, shall enter into a contract for the operation and maintenance of thereferred ports, with an entity or entities duly qualified to perform such tasks, all under terms and conditions acceptable to theBank. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :PA, Section II, Part A, para 1 | Description :Monitor and evaluate project progress and submit reportssemi-annually, with 60 days of the end of the period of review. | Frequency :SemiAnnual

Finance Agreement :PA, Section II, Part A, para 2 | Description :Furnish to the Bank by June 30, 2017, a consolidated mid-termreview for the project and setting out measures to ensure the efficient completion of the project | Due Date :30-Jun-2017

Finance Agreement :PA, Section II, Part B | Description :Prepare and furnish not later than 60 days after the closing periodunaudited financial report; and have financial statements audited and submit audit to the Bank within 6 months of the end of theperiod | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Project Agreement, Section I, Part D, para 1 | Description :Not later than June 30, 2016, Xia’pu County shallensure that the Port Operational and Maintenance Manual has been duly prepared, finalized and submitted to the Bank for its review,and that such manual is subsequently adopted by Xia’pu County. | Due Date :30-Jun-2016
